:"Cook bulgar wheat on hob according to packet instructions."},{"content":"Fluff up bulgar wheat with a fork. Add mint, olive oil, salt, pepper and lemon juice to bulgar wheat then mix using spatula. Serve spiced Quorn on top of some bulgar wheat, with a little yoghurt or harissa on the side."}],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","40m","4 portions"]}